Platform: Nintendo 3DS Released: 2015.02.10

In three days, the moon will fall and the land of Termina will meet with a
terrible fate. Can you save it in time? Relive the world s final 72 hours
solve elaborate puzzles, conquer dungeons, battle giant bosses, and befriend
the doomed people of Termina in one of Nintendo s most suspenseful apocalyptic
adventures ever

The Legend of Zelda: Majora s Mask 3D is a remastered and enhanced version
of the Nintendo classic that s unlike any other Legend of Zelda adventure
In this shadowy tale, a masked Skull Kid drags Link into the world of Termina
where the moon is falling from the sky. Lucky for Termina, Link can reverse
time and relive his last 72 hours in limitless ways. Each time, he ll don any
of his 20+ masks, help different citizens, battle different bosses, and
ultimately change the fate of a world. This is the definitive version of a
dark classic
